# Scope and security

- No authentication, JWT, OAuth or account UI.
- No comments, likes, bookmarks, tags, image uploads, weather, routes, WebSocket, i18n or admin pages.
- No API keys or secrets in frontend source.
- Do not commit `.env`.
- Do not use `v-html` for external or chatbot content unless sanitized.
- Do not store post passwords in state beyond the active request.
- Do not log request bodies containing passwords.
- Keep map attribution visible and use only an approved tile provider.
